{
  "stem": "26728.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was just-- we got to eat real good, and that was such a difference, to sit down and eat a fresh egg, I mean, have two fried eggs with Spam.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Spam-- everybody hated Spam.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I like Spam.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I still like Spam.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And I buy it at the store.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Spam and eggs is full of cholesterol, but I love it.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "OK, so that's about the food.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was-- from then on, it was good food, except-- with few exceptions, I'll say.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "In Frankfurt, the-- about the second day, turned out that most of these men-- and I knew some of them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "My flight leader was one on them-- had been-- had flown L planes.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, the-- the one I showed you the picture of in there, the two seaters.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Liason.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Liaison.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They call him observation-- They call them O planes now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they still have them in the army.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The army uses them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Helicopters, and they use O planes too for the same reason they use him in World War II.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Observation.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you can see, you know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Up high, you can pick targets.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you can see enemy movements and things of that nature, even with the night goggles they have now, you can-- it's really amazing.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I'm glad I didn't have to do all that stuff, but anyhow we were briefed that the-- that the Nazi-- and we had been-- you asked about rumors.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had-- there were rumors, even in the States.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I-- and I have a point I want to make here.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In my unit here at the 70th, there were several Jewish guys from-- and these guys were from-- these were New York Jews, real-- how can I say this?",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
